.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, country, folk, funk, r&b
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, chess, woodworking, drawing
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, april, september, january, august

1. the fan of techno is the person who likes red
2. the fan of country is the person who's birthday is in october
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who likes green
4. the fan of folk is the person who's hobby is collecting
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the old-gold-smoker is the person who's birthday is in august
7. the kools-smoker is the person who likes yellow
8. the person who's hobby is chess is in the middle
9. the fan of funk is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person who's hobby is woodworking
13. the fan of r&b is the parliaments-smoker
14. the fan of funk is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Music-Genre	|   funk	|    folk	|     techno	|    country	|    r&b	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Hobby	|     drawing	|      collecting	|      chess	| woodworking	|     sudoku	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Birthday		|     april	|     january	|     august	|     october	|     september	|
